    {
      "content": "Data Management and Business Analytics",
      "pos": [
        1,
        39
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Managing and analyzing data in the cloud is just as important as it is anywhere else.",
      "pos": [
        41,
        126
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "To let you do this, Azure provides a range of technologies for working with relational and non-relational data.",
      "pos": [
        127,
        238
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This article introduces each of the options.",
      "pos": [
        239,
        283
      ]
    },
