      "pos": [
        13929,
        14020
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "With SSRS on a VM, this can be done using either of two tools: SQL Server Data Tools, part of SQL Server 2012, or its predecessor, Business Intelligence (BI) Development Studio.",
      "pos": [
        14021,
        14198
