      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a name=\"Fig6\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph3\">![</ph>Diagram of table storage<ph id=\"ph4\">][SQL-tblstor]</ph>"
    },
    {
      "content": "Figure 6: Azure Table Storage is a key/value store that provides fast, simple access to large amounts of data.",
      "pos": [
        16195,
        16305
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Like blobs, each table is associated with an Azure storage account.",
      "pos": [
